I have been bullied in high school, been called names, suffered through depression neither did I have many friends, and honestly I’m not ashamed to admit it either. Also, I know for a fact that there are many kids out there who are going through exactly what I have been through and this video is honestly meant for you guys. If you ever feel demotivated or lost or scared, I really wish this video can help guide you through your dark Times. Watch it on High Quality : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=myGbBuHqs-M This a video portraying my journey from High School to where exactly I am right now, how I started? Why I started? Why did I decide to lose weight? How was my School Life Experience? Let me share a memory, this one time in 8th Grade I invited all my classmates to my Birthday, it was during Ramadan so I invited like 19 people to Pizza Hut. Guess what? Only 2 people showed up and I had the other 17 seats reserved, what did I do? I invited all my brother’s friends. Might seem like a Pathetic Incident but it’s the moments like these which MAKE YOU WHO YOU ARE. Make sure to TAG your close friends or Family who might be going through a dark time in their lives. Honestly this is a video which I wanted to bring out for a long time, and I’m Immensely grateful to Salehin Anwar for helping me bring this out, you’re an amazing kid who is going places for sure. A hugeshout to Ekramul Haque for forcing me to start making videos because if this man didn’t Force me to film Burger King that day then I have no idea where I would be right now, I’ll always be grateful to you dost. Director :- Salehin Anwar Assistant D.O.P - Labib Muttaki Studio partner :- Apollo Studios Drone Cinematographer : Sakib UL Alam Sound Designer : - Shehab Shahariar Locations Used : The Courtyard Bazaar, Gulshan Lake Park
